{"id": "1430029980641001482", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "589932567323607102", "author_name": "hiroshi0000", "author_bot": false, "content": "始めて一ヶ月ほどの新米守秘者です。\n融災向けにアイギスを育てたいなと考えているんですが、運用としては覚醒取った上で狂気開放を回して石化やキーチャージを回していく、という感じなんでしょうか？", "timestamp": "2025-10-21T03:08:36.057000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1430042191358595192", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "キーキャラにはならないので覚醒の優先度はやや低い、石化は強いけど結局1ターンの延命でしかないから他のダメージを出せる方が優先度高い", "timestamp": "2025-10-21T03:57:07.319000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["589932567323607102"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1430029980641001482", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1430076167611748403", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "589932567323607102", "author_name": "hiroshi0000", "author_bot": false, "content": "回答ありがとうございます\n覚醒の石化無しだとあとは軟化付与と敵軟化状態の追加効果あたりですし、けっこう厳しそうですね　妨害支援は珍しいので面白そうかなと思ったんですが", "timestamp": "2025-10-21T06:12:07.889000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-21T06:12:18.056000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1430091524049473579", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "いや、その役割でサポートで役にたつよ", "timestamp": "2025-10-21T07:13:09.149000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["589932567323607102"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🙏", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1430076167611748403", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
